"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Happy new year!\\n\\nHere is a very cool idea I have for an NFT collection.\\n\\nHere are the rules\\n\\n1. 366 NFTs (one corresponding to each date on the calendar)\\n2. The person who owns a date NFT can change the text on the NFT (e.g. when Alice and Bob got married, when Charlie was born, when Bitcoin was first launched …)\\n3. The auction to buy a particular day’s NFT starts 48 hours before the date and ends 48 hours after the date in GMT\\n\\nAll the NFTs are displayed on a website along with the text\\n\\n# Website\\n\\n## Display the NFTs\\n\\nA website that has a calendar grid. On each calendar date, there is the date and the text set by the owner.\\n\\nThe NFTs open for auction are highlighted in some way.\\n\\nThese NFTs are displayed using an on-chain SVG generation.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/nosQiyYpevvA34rtRwWQI.png?height=1217&width=1926)\\n\\n## Buy NFT\\n\\nOn tapping on the NFT available for auction, the user should be able to place a bid on chain.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/XhSNpZhKQ5gqeasqjlEFv.png?height=1143&width=1537)\\n\\nThe winner of the bid should be able to withdraw/claim the NFT into their account.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/a1N7jduB6CG_NqP7Si9aZ.png?height=982&width=1361)\\n\\n## Change Text on NFT\\n\\nIf you are the owner of the NFT, and you tap on the date, you can change the text. This text is stored on chain\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/2oX0eaqKxDD2eCIVKUtMX.png?height=985&width=1294)\\n\\n## Wallets\\n\\nMetamask, WalletConnect, Phantom\\n\\n# Marketplace fees\\n\\n3% to you\\n\\n1% to madhavan\\n\\n# Bounty\\n\\nEthereum - 1000 DAI\\n\\nSolana - 5.5 SOL\\n\\nDeadline 15 Jan 2022\",\"timestamp\":1641377338,\"title\":\"Request to build - A calendar NFT\"},\"digest\":\"UtxQvtfWyUz6xCAP3R90GjGsSEq9wGX_2Gs9QOzX06o\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xa2dDFc8a6C1F8868B80F2747D04532a6cDE9804d\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DDhNljfF5mUscdPBA-XjBWovdbD4xSYuf6D3RDgu3mI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ovUJpccYf30QqMREGLNKP3Z1RSTrs_mlluMBjZtaWcY\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"u-RvqFVL5bzZGv9-7MB3jkoQgpcm8AqGE-Gkvp6VbuMFEWEaExu0EKo5c_HVYfmwCMCLxfJfswokHPU80sNYAQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x23f5dfe94b85aa901c2ab4179b9bc2ab44c44ffcf7751f53ae88174906fcd9081ab0bc824ba8ab7a802f0c05d8ec389b4328cdf473e15e5b467098d26d0d68f61b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"DDhNljfF5mUscdPBA-XjBWovdbD4xSYuf6D3RDgu3mI\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"ovUJpccYf30QqMREGLNKP3Z1RSTrs_mlluMBjZtaWcY\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"7T_0VpD8CP1-1XZGkMx5lDNcGQXX6LCQx6sh88R52D0\"}"